From 8ab2ff108ce59f2308142ac1297ac4b22bba2169 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 07:04:29 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 4/8] Add PDF viewer stream shim

A PDF asked, "Where is my stream?"
We packed a note inside its dream.
The viewer knocks, the logs reply,
Then chrome:// ghosts go drifting by.
